name: Higher Beings
description:
You hear a weird voice in your head. Suddenly, you are in the middle of nowhere and have a life changing decision to make...

Instructions

WASD or Arrow Keys to move

Space to jump, double press to double jump

Credits

Art - https://0x72.itch.io/16x16-industrial-tileset

Font - https://www.fontspace.com/timeburner-font-f15111 

You might experience some weird clipping going on with some of the art, I realized it but I didn't know how to fix it and I was already pressed for time.
